    body
        .container
            .row.splash
                .twelve.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                    div(style="background: url('/images/IntergalacticLabs3.png') no-repeat center; background-size: contain; height: 80vh; max-width: 600px; margin: auto;")
                    .tagline(style="height: 20vh;")
                        a.down(href="#about")
                            div Goodbye Earth
                            div ▼
            .row
                .twelve.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                    h3#about A community for <a href="#golden">golden</a> future

        .wow
            .container
                .row
                    .four.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                        a(href="#lunarbase")
                            .feature.u-max-full-width(style="background-image: url('/images/spacesuit-gold.png')")
                            h4 Lunar Infrastructure
                        p
                            | We are building roads and power grids on the moon for research stations.
                            | The goal is to give scientists and private space companies the utilities they need to extend
                            | their operations to the moon.
                        a(href="#lunarbase") Read More
                    .four.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                        a(href="#openecosystem")
                            .feature.u-max-full-width(style="background-image: url('/images/leaf-fractal-gold.png')")
                            h4 Open Ecosystem
                        p
                            | We are open-sourcing a
                            | <strong>next-generation human sustenance program</strong>
                            | built for bringing the best of earth to the rest of the galaxy.
                        a(href="#openecosystem") Read More
                    .four.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                        a(href="#experimentalphysics")
                            .feature.u-max-full-width(style="background-image: url('/images/wormhole-gold.png')")
                            h4 Physics
                        p
                            | Conventional propulsion might not be enough to
                            | extend human presence beyond our solar system.  We are trying to
                            | <strong>understand and manipulate gravity and space-time</strong>
                            | so that we can one day effortlessly traverse the universe.
                        a(href="#experimentalphysics") Read More
                .row
                    .twelve.columns.u-textAlignCenter
                        button.button-primary.button-join Follow Intergalactic Labs



